Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my stupid son...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Goodbye Drum Island!\NI'm Going Out to Sea!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:01:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry blossoms, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... is Chopper okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave him alone for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's experiencing what it's like\Nto set out on a journey as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he is about to leave the\Nisland he's spent his entire life in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving, Doctor... Doctorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My adventure... is finally starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a joyous day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon is out and the\Ncherry blossoms have bloomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Hey, Chopper!\NYou son of a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna\Nbe in a daze like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here and sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, stick these\Nchopsticks up your nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, what a grand nighttime\Nview of cherry blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we not have a\Nparty at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made friends with\Nsome really crazy guys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. They're over the top,\Nbut since you're one of us now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo! What were you doing\Nfrozen in the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably slipped or something.\NHe's a clumsy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, Mr. Bushido!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says that the guy named Zoro was\Nswimming in the river and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He thought Zoro was in trouble so he\Njumped into the river and got frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony-kun, you can understand\Nwhat Karoo is saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm an animal by nature,\Nso I can talk with animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk with animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's incredible, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to do that along\Nwith your medical skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy! Praising me like that wouldn't\Nmake me feel happy! You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Nami, what do\Nyou mean by "medical skills"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper is a doctor... a first-class one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with all the medical skills\Nhammered into him by Dr. Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! You're a doctor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good Lord! What did you think Chopper\Nwas when you asked him to join us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A seven-form transforming\Ninteresting reindeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...! Darn it! I forgot to bring my\Nmedical tools since I left in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be... Then what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in the sleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come? Didn't you prepare\Nfor the trip by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:05:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all... she knew\Neverything you were thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful person she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah! I got snot on the chopsticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah...\N--Ah! I got snot on the chopsticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper, you try it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... When you're reminiscing...\NRight, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You bastard!\N--Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You bastard!\N--Well, I'd like to introduce
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our new friend to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji! Go!\N--Tony Tony Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He'll be our ship's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I...\N--He'll be our ship's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I...\N--To celebrate his coming on board...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Listen to me, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had this much fun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's toast to our new friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they've left the island by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A reindeer with a first-rate heart\Nand first-rate skills as a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the cherry blossoms that Hiriluk put\Nhis life into really did lead to a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd have to be just that clumsy\Nreindeer going out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid... acting like he's all grown up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be a fine ship's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what're you gonna do from here on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was... working as the Captain\Nof the Security Guard under Wapol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have to atone for that sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about leaving this land
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and entrusting this new\Ncountry to the citizens...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... going to do that then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I've come to realize that\Nleaving isn't the only way of atoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country is breaking\Nthe shackles of monarchy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a new country made by the\Ncitizens' hands is about to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There may be something I can do for\Nthe birth of this country by staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that that is indeed\Na way for me to atone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph, you youngster...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do have a heart\Nto care for the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A heart to care for the country, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I once learned it from\Na girl who was only ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:12.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Holy Land of Marie Jois"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... World Summit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a tiresome, worthless event.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the Drum Kingdom\Nwill be okay like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rift between the king\Nand citizens keeps growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the king of the Alabasta Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Nefertari Cobra-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the king of Alabasta,\Nfamed for his benevolence and wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revolutionist Dragon...\NThis man's ideologies are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very clear that he'll become a\Nbig enemy to us, the World Government,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in 5-6 years and stand in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... How ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I govern my country so that my people\Nwon't be led astray by a revolutionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys wanna capture him,\Ngo ahead and do it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think the World Summit is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Act more responsibly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Nefertari Cobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! What an unpleasant\Nconference that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the daughter of\Nthat detestable Cobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me. If I'm not mistaken,\Nyou're the princess of Lord Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a poor child, to be the\Ndaughter of that hopeless king.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Igaram! I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, too, for bumping into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the World Summit where kings gather,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even a minor argument can trigger a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tolerates this situation knowing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already at this young age...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! What an annoying brat.\NLet's go, Dalton.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were magnificent, Vivi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess' heart to care for the country...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her nobility hasn't changed one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How magnificent she turned out to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heart to care for the\Ncountry still remains in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us do something...\Nto help this new country...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiriluk...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country will surely be reborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like your son, Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san! This is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered something serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him! The Straw Hat\Npirate who beat Wapol!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 30 million-berry bounty is\Non his head... They are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? They're quite the rogues, aren't they...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you find this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I completely forgot\Nto report it to you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about a week ago, a man who\Nappeared to be a traveler
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,suddenly appeared in Robelle Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an unusual day where no snow fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know where he landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this guy said that\Nhe was after Blackbeard,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the pirate that attacked this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once he realized that\NBlackbeard was long gone, he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me ask you one more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has a pirate wearing\Na straw hat come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we said we didn't know,\Nhe showed the wanted poster and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this guy comes here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he does...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tell him that I'll wait for him\Nin Alabasta for just 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait! What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell him that when he comes,\Nhe'll know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please catch him!\NHe just ate and skipped on the bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Well then,\Ntell him, okay? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll wait for 10 days in Alabasta... huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Dr. Kureha, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Gol D. Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D? Are you talking about Gold Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what he's called these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my reindeer went with\Nan extraordinary guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... the will of D... was still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! And the ones who go on\Nadventures on that huge sea are pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:14:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Pirates are\Nincredible after all. Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a seagull.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a seagull that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Seagull!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I was right. It is a seagull.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to discuss that!\NIt's coming because you called it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! It's a great adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't become bird food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! It's terrible! A bird ate Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for playing around!\NLuffy's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say he wanted our help?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's no problem.\NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Propeller!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji! I've got some meat! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you guys sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna fix this situation?\NI had a good hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can have some decent meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's the matter, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Pirates are...\NPirates are incredible after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Incredible, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship is arriving at Alabasta soon.\NWe don't have time to play around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's Alabasta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the country that Vivi's father governs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rogue named Crocodile is trying\Nto take over Alabasta right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that Crocodile is one of\Nthe Seven Warlords of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven Warlords of the Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the pirates authorized\Nby the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are authorized by the Government?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They're overwhelmingly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, they crush other pirates one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Government authorizes\Nthem to crush pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.88,0:16:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile, huh...? I can't wait to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile is a hero in Alabasta because\Nhe crushes the pirates that attack towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only his public face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind the scenes, he is pulling strings\Nto cause a civil war in Alabasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to take over Alabasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens... My father... No one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then! In any case, all we have\Nto do is beat up that Crocodile, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If we can first stop the\Ncivil war and expel Baroque Works...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baroque Works...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... Yeah, you don't know\Nabout them either, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I can't\Nquite understand, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baroque Works has a complicated system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system itself is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, at the top, there's a boss, Crocodile...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in other words, Mr. 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're 12 agents and one animal who\Nreceive orders from the boss directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of the 12 agents operates\Nseparately as a pair with a female agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 1 and Miss Double Finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 2 doesn't have a partner, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 3 is the candle man we\Nmet in Little Garden, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He was paired up\Nwith Miss Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 4 is paired up\Nwith Miss Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about\Nthese two, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that snot guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 5, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. His snot is a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 5's entire body is a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Valentine has the powers\Nof the Kilo Kilo Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that woman who can change\Nher weight freely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:18:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Mr. 1 through Mr. 5,\Nthey're called officer agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all have the powers of a devil fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they work only on\Nreally important missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Mr. 6 through Mr. 13, their job\Nis fund raising for the company
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by leading the employees at\Nthe entrance of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, there was\Na strange monkey and chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Mr. 13 and Miss Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a punishment squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their main job is to punish\Nthose who fail missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than these people,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there're 200 subordinates called\N"Billions" under the officer agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and 1800 subordinates called\N"Millions" under the frontier agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the secret crime\Nsyndicate, Baroque Works.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means... 1800 plus 200, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're 2000 subordinates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2000!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I understand it very well now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, all we have to do\Nis beat up that Crocodile, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Baroque Works' last big job\Nis to take over Alabasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the rest of those "officer agents" will all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gather in Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Then, in any case,\Nwe'll beat that Crocodile guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.\NYou keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un, deux, ora! Un, deux, krah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, Mr. 2, Bon Clay-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break!\NWho do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Bon Clay-sama,\Na Baroque Works' officer agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's so fearful that even a\Ncrying child will become quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! You navigator, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me! What's 0-chan's order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Mr. 3 on the direct route\Nbetween Alabasta and Little Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you do know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct route means going\Nin a straight line, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we traveled straight from\NAlabasta to this Little Garden, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got to Little Garden\Nwithout meeting Mr. 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it mean that you\Nguys missed Mr. 3's ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... that can't be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you saying that\Nit was because I'm stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Mr. 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:25.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bon Clay"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we can't be failing in the\N"beating puny Mr. 3 mission"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at an important time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we did, Mr. 1 and his\Npartner will come to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna be my prey,\Nthen look for Mr. 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super full speed! We're heading\Nto Alabasta on the Swanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen! Don't overlook\Neven a single small ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 2, Bon Clay-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Pirates are attacking\Ntowns in the Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they know this\Ncountry has Crocodile?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows... Sir Crocodile...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a country where riots are going\Non is an easy target for pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I have to do a good job\Nfor my public position, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How kind of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seven Warlords of the Sea\Nare pirates who crush other pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heroes to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this sleepless town\Nhas dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today forth,\Nsomething's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can start fresh,\Nsince I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by having you by my side,\NI feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far I can go,\Ntowards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off in the distance it shines,\Nencompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, make something, you damn cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.95,0:23:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't because a certain idiot\Nate all the food.
